Michael Derks has left FxPro Financial
Services Ltd. where he served as a chief strategist, according
to an e-mailed statement sent from his personal account.  Prior to joining FxPro in 2010, Derks worked for Arch
Financial Products LLP, Deutsche Bank AG, Nomura International
Plc and Rothschild Asset Management Inc., according to data
compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporters on this story:
